              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Very easy — only a scale needed</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Requires a tape measure and careful technique</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Accuracy for Athletes</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Poor — overestimates fat in muscular people</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Better — accounts for body shape</td>
            </tr>
